      • connectToServerUsingProtocol

        private static boolean connectToServerUsingProtocol(java.lang.String ipAndPort)
        Connects to the given server (IP and Port) using an empty (no) password. Other than connectToServer(String) and connectToServer(String, String), this method uses the samp:// protocol to connect to make the samp launcher connect to the server.
        Parameters:
        ipAndPort - the server to connect to
        Returns:
        true if it was most likely successful
